      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Engineered for performance, it utilizes individual throttle bodies and a variable M differential lock to provide exceptional throttle response and corner-exit traction. This unit has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a top-tier VANOS service to maintain valve timing precision. The suspension maintains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, offering a communicative chassis feel through every apex. While the exterior reflects its history as a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the mechanical vitals are strong, with consistent compression across all cylinders and a crisp, linear power band. Ideal for an enthusiast seeking a mechanically sound icon that is ready for spirited weekend excursions.",
